stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Scheduled: patient creates appointment

    Scheduled --> Confirmed: doctor confirms consultation
    Scheduled --> Rescheduled: patient or doctor updates date or time
    Scheduled --> Cancelled: patient or doctor cancels

    Rescheduled --> Confirmed: doctor confirms updated slot
    Rescheduled --> Rescheduled: patient or doctor changes slot again
    Rescheduled --> Cancelled: patient or doctor cancels

    Confirmed --> Completed: doctor marks consultation complete
    Confirmed --> Rescheduled: patient or doctor changes slot
    Confirmed --> Cancelled: patient or doctor cancels

    Completed --> [*]
    Cancelled --> [*]